des:
FAME FM Qatar is a Top 40 Arabic entertainment radio station in Qatar. It's hip, trendy, like no other, and full of life

Our music is Levantine, Arabic, English, and International from Levant, UK, and US charts

We are covering all Qatar through FM waves (99.9 Mhz), and the World through Streaming

FAME FM Qatar has an application on Apple, Android, and Windows playstores. In addition, it exists on most of the steaming radios applications

FAME FM Qatar is a Madanat Media Production company registered in Qatar, Jordan, and United Arab Emirates
